snippet.title: Purposely Curious Podcast
snippet.description: Welcome to the Purposely Curious Podcast YouTube page. Join your host Mary as we bring you interviews and discussions on life's most curious topics. Our guests come from all walks of life with expertises, specialties, and life experiences as they open up and share their knowledge on life's most interesting curiosities. Find us also on most podcast platforms.
